column1: Notifiable Disease Surveillance Data by District Health Board April 2016

column3: Cases_ and current rate_ for April 2016 by District Health Board_

column1: _ Current rate is based on the cumulative total for the 12 months up to and including April 2016 expressed as cases per 100,000. This includes cases still under investigation.
_ Further data are available from the local Medical Officer of Health.
_ Rates are based on report date. This may not be a good indicator of newly incident cases as a high proportion of notifications have substantial reporting delays.
